curl https://<domain>/v2/user/authenticate
-H "Content-Type: application/json"
-X POST

Description: This endpoint is to be called when system demands for a valid jwtoken

````
body (sample)
{
    *"email": "abubakar@yahoo.com",
    *"salt": "k9hRg8FdcpfK"
}
````
````
body (description)
{
    "email": "Email address of customer",
    "salt": "To be generated by the application and stored against the customer and used as authentication password"
}
````

````
response (sample)
{
    "code": 200,
    "status": "OK",
    "message": "Token generate, use in your request headers with the key jwtoken",
    "result": {
        "token": "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6ImJhc2lsbUB5YWguY29tIiwic2FsdCI6IlJwRWxZbUNyeiIsInRpbWUiOjE2NjI1MTg1NTd9.dV4Tmxajo1NNPxlBE7S7cfhl2PD6024ltz6Z6hki7fc",
    }
} 
````